Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.76,0:01:40.99,Vinland-tips,NTP,0,0,0,,註：諾森布里亞，英格蘭七國時代裡其中一個盎格魯-撒克遜王國，\N領土包括今英格蘭北部和蘇格蘭東南部，維京人入侵不列顛島後併入英格蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.52,0:01:45.12,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那一天是星期六
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.73,0:01:48.75,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,維京人會在星期六洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.03,0:01:56.90,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,英格蘭人知道他們有這種習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.28,0:02:08.38,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,敵…敵人來襲了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.53,0:02:17.55,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,全都燒光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.69,0:02:19.42,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,女人和小孩也不要放過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.84,0:02:22.29,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,趕盡殺絕 這是國王的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.84,0:02:22.84,Vinland-tips,NTP,0,0,0,,註：1002年，英格蘭國王“無策者”埃塞爾雷德二世下令屠殺所有在英格蘭的丹麥人。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.13,0:02:41.01,Vinland-title,,0,0,0,,{\blur7\fad(695,550)\pos(1677.867,123.867)}#02 劍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.27,0:02:43.10,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,支撐住
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.34,0:02:44.72,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,現在才是決勝負的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.07,0:02:48.85,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,好 斯諾雷被我殺死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.32,0:02:50.50,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.19,0:02:53.40,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,好 槍兵隊 上前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.61,0:02:54.82,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,突擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.27,0:03:05.40,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,戰場移到那邊去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.27,0:03:09.65,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 為什麼我老是一下子就被幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.17,0:03:13.48,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,屍體不能說話 托爾芬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.27,0:03:17.78,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你總是最先死掉的那個呢 法克希
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:25.08,Vinland-pronunciation,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(975,1000)}                             Valhalla
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:25.08,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為只要去到天堂的英靈神殿 每天都能吃上肉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:25.08,Vinland-tips,NTP,0,0,0,,註：英靈神殿，北歐神話中的天堂，在人間戰死的戰士靈魂將被帶至此處享受永恆的幸福。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.48,0:03:29.33,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是強大的戰士是不能進入英靈神殿的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.45,0:03:32.92,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.63,0:03:39.58,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽和姐姐能去英靈神殿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.68,0:03:46.27,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,被幹掉了嗎 托爾芬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.48,0:03:48.85,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,躺在雪地上裝死 可能要感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.03,0:03:54.66,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,明天出發？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.89,0:03:57.57,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,真好 真好 這次要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.02,0:03:58.98,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,去挪威
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.13,0:04:00.24,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,但我可不是去玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.86,0:04:02.28,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去做生意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.87,0:04:07.02,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,把毛織物和毛皮帶去換葡萄酒什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.38,0:04:08.70,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.33,0:04:10.25,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.36,0:04:12.88,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,「那」是什麼意思 別說的那麼輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.87,0:04:14.80,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,小氣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.98,0:04:17.42,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是撞上浮冰我可不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:23.02,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我想在今年結束之前喝上葡萄酒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.59,0:04:28.21,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,和我故國的鄉親們一起喝葡萄酒 慶祝耶穌基督的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.59,0:04:28.21,Vinland-tips,NTP,0,0,0,,註：雷夫·埃里克森是挪威出身的基督教徒，當時的挪威正在逐漸接納基督教。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:32.14,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我父親喜歡蜂蜜酒 不如讓他分點給你？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.69,0:04:36.22,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,喝葡萄酒才有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.78,0:04:40.55,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我還以為這個村子裡有葡萄酒的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:49.42,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,托爾芬 麻煩跑一趟給你父親傳個話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.07,0:04:52.74,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,說來了一艘戰船
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.83,0:05:06.73,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣如何 師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.86,0:05:08.54,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,這次應該不會漏了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:10.48,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,放點水進去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,0:05:16.02,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,這活真難
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.30,0:05:18.52,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你太用力了 托爾茲先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.57,0:05:19.98,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.27,0:05:21.51,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:24.11,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我在這 托爾芬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:25.76,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:27.75,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,又有戰船來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.94,0:05:29.30,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,很大的一艘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:49.07,Vinland-pronunciation,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1210,1000)}                         Thors the Troll
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:49.07,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,他們說讓我們交出「戰鬼」托爾茲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.15,0:05:50.01,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,之後就一直站在那裡沒動過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.59,0:05:53.13,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,他們說的是托爾茲先生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:54.53,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,巨人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.93,0:05:57.71,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不過他們應該不是什麼等閒之輩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.14,0:06:00.90,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,跟哈夫丹手下的那幫地痞完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.04,0:06:04.06,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,托爾茲先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:06.88,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那些人是不是要攻打我們村
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.16,0:06:13.66,Vinland-tips - pronunciation,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(140,0)}Jomsvikings
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.16,0:06:12.64,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,約姆斯的戰士們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.16,0:06:13.66,Vinland-tips,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(10,20)}註：約姆斯維京人，10-11世紀活躍在北歐的海盜集團，有時會接受成為封建領主的僱傭兵。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.01,0:06:14.42,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:27.66,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,他們在向托爾茲先生行禮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.29,0:06:31.11,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到你竟會找到這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.58,0:06:33.90,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,弗洛基
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.67,0:06:39.47,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,挪威遠征以來我們就沒再見過面呢 托爾茲閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.62,0:06:44.92,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到您竟然藏身於此等偏遠之地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.74,0:06:48.05,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,說重點吧 弗洛基
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.84,0:06:51.93,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 首先請允許我們登陸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.98,0:06:56.52,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你們說托爾茲先生會是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.13,0:07:00.29,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我只聽說過他年輕時打過仗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:02.18,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你聲音太大了 亞雷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.26,0:07:06.42,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟他不怎麼喜歡談論自己的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.62,0:07:08.84,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 也讓我看一看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.06,0:07:11.46,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,他好像說了「約姆的戰士們」這個詞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.93,0:07:13.01,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你聽說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.16,0:07:14.16,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:17.60,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺爸爸好像生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.83,0:07:22.69,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,據說是趁他們洗澡的時候發動奇襲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.21,0:07:28.50,Vinland-pronunciation,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(560,1000)}Danelaw
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.21,0:07:28.50,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,在丹麥區各地 大量丹麥人被英格蘭軍隊殺害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.21,0:07:28.50,Vinland-tips,NTP,0,0,0,,註：丹麥區，英格蘭東北部由丹麥人統治的地區，根據878年威塞克斯王國和丹麥軍隊簽訂的合約設立
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.45,0:07:31.07,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,被害者當中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.40,0:07:36.60,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,就有丹麥國王斯韋恩的妹妹 岡希爾德公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.34,0:07:39.56,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,為妹妹報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.13,0:07:42.93,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,斯韋恩國王找到了一個很好的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.30,0:07:45.67,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,很快將會有一場大戰發生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.85,0:07:47.93,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,輪到我們這些戰士出場了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.45,0:07:49.26,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,戰爭？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:49.65,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,噓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.33,0:07:53.51,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,約姆戰士團將和丹麥軍聯手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:57.43,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,待到春季 就會開始向英格蘭進軍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.69,0:08:00.03,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你們隨意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.38,0:08:02.56,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是世界最北端的小村而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.05,0:08:07.38,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,北海那邊的大國紛爭都和我們無關
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.83,0:08:11.98,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,這可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.33,0:08:14.43,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的首領西格瓦迪的命令是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.73,0:08:17.48,Vinland-pronunciation,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1050,1000)}               Jomsborg
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.73,0:08:17.48,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,全體艦隊在約姆斯堡集結
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.73,0:08:17.73,Vinland-tips,NTP,0,0,0,,註：傳說中約姆斯維京人的大本營，推測位於今波蘭北岸的沃林島。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.70,0:08:18.93,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有例外
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.86,0:08:21.17,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,您明白其中的意思嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.42,0:08:25.84,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,即便那個人是逃兵也不例外
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:29.27,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,逃兵？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.80,0:08:36.93,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,尤姆斯戰士團大隊長 「戰鬼」托爾茲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.15,0:08:39.14,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,此次戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.59,0:08:43.17,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,您也要參加
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.67,0:08:57.08,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,托爾茲閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.28,0:09:01.01,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,這次我們首領可是非常寬宏大量了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.30,0:09:05.32,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,15年前下落失蹤的您
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.41,0:09:08.20,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,在這次戰爭正式返回前線
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.53,0:09:12.88,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣一來就對你既往不咎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.02,0:09:17.88,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我們首領對您的能力重視到了如此地步
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.07,0:09:22.74,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,為了說這件事 沒必要坐戰船來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.06,0:09:25.20,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,村裡的人們都很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.37,0:09:31.15,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那位托爾茲閣下真是變了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.66,0:09:34.48,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,還是說 是這個村子改變了他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.52,0:09:35.94,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.03,0:09:36.80,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.86,0:09:39.24,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.86,0:09:42.04,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,這村子不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.39,0:09:43.92,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,從孩子們的外表就能看出來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.39,0:09:48.45,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,他們應該從來都沒有經歷過戰亂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.03,0:09:56.67,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,聽到了嗎 要打仗了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.77,0:09:57.58,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.62,0:09:58.70,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是第一次聽別人談這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.03,0:10:03.29,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,他們可是特地漂洋過海來邀請託爾茲先生的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.43,0:10:05.81,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你老爸真的好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.07,0:10:11.18,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不過他們肯帶上我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.42,0:10:13.44,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你肯定不行 那麼弱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.51,0:10:14.77,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.86,0:10:16.93,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是要足夠強才可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.11,0:10:19.65,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,這方面我應該沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.11,0:10:22.52,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你們都沒有砍過人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.75,0:10:25.25,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,有沒有這種經歷…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.19,0:10:27.14,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.33,0:10:39.01,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不是個沒本事的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.65,0:10:43.25,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果您不打算參加這次戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.63,0:10:47.69,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我就不能完成任務 我們首領也保不住面子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.40,0:10:52.05,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話 我實在沒辦法空手而歸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.39,0:10:58.03,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,您能理解吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.17,0:11:07.69,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,約姆戰士團
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.62,0:11:13.66,Vinland-pronunciation,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(865,1000)}  Wendland
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.62,0:11:13.66,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,他們的基地在溫德蘭的海港城市 約姆斯堡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.62,0:11:13.62,Vinland-tips,NTP,0,0,0,,註：溫德蘭，在中世紀指波羅的海南岸一帶地區，因西斯拉夫人遷居至此而得名。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.43,0:11:17.89,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到托爾茲以前是個約姆戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.27,0:11:19.36,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,他們很強嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.78,0:11:20.71,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,很強
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.85,0:11:22.03,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為太過強大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.21,0:11:26.45,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,溫德蘭國王都不敢向他們徵稅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.26,0:11:30.22,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,他們自詡為北海最強的軍團
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.41,0:11:32.86,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,收隊 全員回到船上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.19,0:11:36.50,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,收隊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.11,0:11:45.30,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.37,0:11:46.57,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,真讓人不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.78,0:11:48.97,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.13,0:11:54.91,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了 村民們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.37,0:11:57.89,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是約姆戰士團的弗洛基
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.87,0:11:59.85,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我奉首領之命令
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.90,0:12:03.80,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,為邀請勇士托爾茲·斯諾雷遜援助我軍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.81,0:12:04.91,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,來到了這片土地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.54,0:12:06.68,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,勇士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.14,0:12:10.71,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,托爾茲閣下接受了我們首領的請求
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.79,0:12:13.94,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,並答應向我軍提供一艘戰船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.45,0:12:15.93,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,有意願參戰者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.93,0:12:19.88,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,隨托爾茲閣下一同前來約姆斯堡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.65,0:12:29.04,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 托爾茲殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.36,0:12:31.84,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,日後在戰場上再會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.22,0:12:40.16,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,打仗啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.97,0:12:46.83,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,幾…幾十年不遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.69,0:12:49.32,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,好咧 大幹一番吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:51.87,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,戰死沙場才是男人的夙願
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.97,0:12:53.11,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是下定決心開幹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.17,0:12:54.71,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,明天就要準備戰船了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:02.75,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒能拒絕掉呢 托爾茲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.04,0:13:06.26,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,把村子捲進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.20,0:13:11.23,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,從前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.33,0:13:14.08,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我以殺人為生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.25,0:13:16.66,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.61,0:13:20.18,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,有一天我突然厭惡了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.35,0:13:24.48,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,無論是殺人 還是被殺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:29.08,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我從戰場上逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.12,0:13:37.95,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,本以為自己假裝戰死 已經瞞過他們了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.39,0:13:40.18,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼就再逃一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.17,0:13:44.00,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.06,0:13:46.60,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,他們就會轉而報復這個村子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.68,0:13:48.60,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,約姆戰士團有規定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.94,0:13:50.85,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,絕不放過一個逃兵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.70,0:14:03.47,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,是時候和自己過去所做的一切做個了結
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.81,0:14:12.33,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,好 要拉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.62,0:14:14.39,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.98,0:14:20.49,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,用力拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.16,0:14:25.39,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,雷夫大叔你不是今天出航嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.68,0:14:27.39,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,托爾茲來拜託我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.66,0:14:30.41,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我的船和這艘戰船一起結隊出航
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.50,0:14:31.65,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.71,0:14:33.71,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,確實這樣更安全
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.85,0:14:36.91,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,出現意外的話我們會保護你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.64,0:14:41.99,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那可真是可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.31,0:14:43.77,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,加把勁拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.15,0:14:46.60,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.88,0:14:49.51,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,一個個都只是嚮往戰爭的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.50,0:14:52.35,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.76,0:14:56.24,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,好過分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.65,0:15:00.40,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 托爾芬那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.49,0:15:01.72,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,圍住他 圍住他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.23,0:15:04.44,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.96,0:15:06.85,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了 成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.95,0:15:07.57,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,把托爾芬…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.80,0:15:10.29,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.36,0:15:11.80,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什麼 裝死啊 托爾芬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.91,0:15:13.02,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛你被幹掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.24,0:15:14.55,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,要遵守規則
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.70,0:15:15.90,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.63,0:15:19.27,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.43,0:15:20.36,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.13,0:15:22.48,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,等下啊 托爾芬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:23.31,Vinland-text - top,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼走掉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.33,0:15:31.17,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,好 舉起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.90,0:15:37.42,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,好 再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.14,0:15:39.18,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,托爾茲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.69,0:15:41.56,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,能過來看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.83,0:15:46.14,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.46,0:15:47.41,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,骨折了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.76,0:15:49.71,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,小孩之間的遊戲算玩過火了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.31,0:15:53.50,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來一個月都要包紮固定好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.77,0:15:55.58,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,麻煩你了 托爾茲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.91,0:15:57.23,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,是托爾芬幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.60,0:15:59.35,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙最近很暴躁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:00.95,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,下手不知輕重
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.03,0:16:02.90,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不會再找他玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.03,0:16:04.35,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.62,0:16:05.51,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,是我家的孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.43,0:16:09.42,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那真是對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:11.06,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,回去會好好說教他的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:13.67,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.88,0:16:15.31,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,小孩之間的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.75,0:16:17.47,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,但他還只有六歲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.90,0:16:20.69,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,能傷到比他大四五歲的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:22.28,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,很厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.70,0:16:24.54,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子能成長為一名出色的戰士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.70,0:16:27.63,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是繼承了你的血脈啊 托爾茲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.22,0:16:42.19,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,這一套都給我嗎 老爹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.31,0:16:45.35,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,從爺爺那一輩的傳家武具
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.52,0:16:47.12,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,去盡情戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:48.17,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,亞雷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.57,0:16:50.84,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,很帥嘛 亞雷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.41,0:16:52.57,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,也看下我的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.19,0:16:56.19,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,據說是能一擊砍下馬頭的名器啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.69,0:16:57.64,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.89,0:16:59.48,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,要去狩獵當然是用槍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.88,0:17:01.55,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那要來比一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.85,0:17:04.30,Vinland-text - top,NTP,0,0,0,,你笑什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.48,0:17:08.09,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你個小毛孩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.23,0:17:10.97,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,別動不動就到處亂丟東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.03,0:17:12.36,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 聽到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.67,0:17:14.46,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不收拾好我就丟掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.70,0:17:15.51,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.81,0:17:17.39,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,丟就丟 已經不需要了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.20,0:17:22.76,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什麼啊 在倉庫裡翻來翻去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.48,0:17:24.90,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我們家的武器在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.17,0:17:26.40,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 武器?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.25,0:17:29.25,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要一把武器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.84,0:17:30.72,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,有武器的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.68,0:17:34.07,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你難不成想要成為戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.14,0:17:36.89,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,然後坐上父親的船出航嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.64,0:17:39.22,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,醜話說在前頭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.43,0:17:40.86,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你這是白費力氣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.06,0:17:42.49,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,像你這樣的小不點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.07,0:17:47.92,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,托爾芬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.73,0:18:35.12,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.88,0:18:47.72,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.83,0:18:48.93,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 尤爾瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.55,0:18:55.26,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,想要劍嗎 托爾芬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.54,0:18:58.64,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,劍是用來殺人的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.44,0:19:02.82,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你接下來想殺誰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.66,0:19:06.96,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,敵…敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.95,0:19:10.78,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你的敵人是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.28,0:19:16.19,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,比…比如哈夫丹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.67,0:19:22.47,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,好好聽我說 托爾芬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.76,0:19:31.38,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒有任何敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.61,0:19:33.66,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,無論是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.07,0:19:35.65,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,都沒有任何敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.90,0:19:44.30,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不存在任何允許你肆意傷害的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.76,0:19:51.02,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你這樣講很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.51,0:19:54.42,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為父親明天就要去打仗了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.02,0:19:56.85,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,是要去殺死敵人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.34,0:20:00.73,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經不是小孩了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.20,0:20:02.92,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,父親在說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.34,0:20:04.68,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是我也明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.14,0:20:07.91,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,托爾芬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.70,0:20:10.04,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 托爾芬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.32,0:20:11.24,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,有破綻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.35,0:20:12.36,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,好危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.07,0:20:15.91,Vinland-text - top,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 出血了 血
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.58,0:20:23.41,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,赫爾加
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.85,0:20:25.62,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.08,0:20:30.86,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個孩子 拜託你照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.53,0:20:51.37,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,西稍偏北方向 微風
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.73,0:20:53.32,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,徐波不驚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.68,0:20:57.24,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天早上奧丁神心情很好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.07,0:21:00.57,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,這個早晨 很適合出航
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.37,0:21:13.33,Vinland-picture,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(970,900)\fad(544,500)\blur2.5}法羅群島 斯特萊默島
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.37,0:21:13.33,Vinland-picture-pronunciation,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(845,850)\fad(544,500)\blur2.5}Faroe Islands
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.37,0:21:13.33,Vinland-picture-pronunciation,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1050,850)\fad(544,500)\blur2.5}Streymoy
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.99,0:21:16.36,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,好 你說的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.56,0:21:18.10,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我用左手扔中的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.17,0:21:20.06,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那桶酒就是我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.42,0:21:21.42,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:22.42,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,扔中了再說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.42,0:21:23.01,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,主啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.58,0:21:25.47,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我扔了哦 基督教的禿驢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.85,0:21:27.20,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,敢躲開就殺掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.39,0:21:32.87,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙 竟然躲開了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.92,0:21:34.01,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛躲開了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.03,0:21:35.74,Vinland-text - top,NTP,0,0,0,,殺了你 我要殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.08,0:21:36.66,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,讓開 下一個是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.75,0:21:41.98,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,神父大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.38,0:21:45.10,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了不要躲開
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.32,0:21:47.10,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,是你太菜了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.66,0:21:50.94,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,約姆的大兄弟們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.26,0:21:53.25,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你們不來一杯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.58,0:21:58.97,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 真是拘禮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.12,0:21:59.97,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,別管他們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.42,0:22:02.58,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,便宜酒不合他們口味
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.35,0:22:07.75,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,扔中腳得幾分來著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.85,0:22:10.85,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,和以往一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.85,0:22:12.89,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你的手下還是這麼沒品
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.46,0:22:14.53,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,阿謝拉特
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.88,0:22:18.07,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,他們只是不喜歡基督教徒而已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.49,0:22:19.81,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,弗洛基老爺
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.97,0:22:21.69,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,比起這個
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.03,0:22:24.25,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,還是快說說工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.58,0:22:26.78,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,手下們和我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.40,0:22:30.60,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,在這鳥不拉屎的地方都等到煩悶了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.84,0:22:33.54,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,大體上沒有變動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.75,0:22:38.90,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,報酬是五磅黃金
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.22,0:22:42.50,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,必須要拿他的屍體來換
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.28,0:22:47.31,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,他的船和貨物任你處置
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.18,0:22:52.25,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,殺了托爾茲
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——————ED——————
