Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.72,0:23:06.33,Vinland-ed-ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(300,300)}好似屋中盛開的小花
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.42,0:23:12.41,Vinland-ed-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(300,300)}強く確かな意思を掲げ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.42,0:23:12.41,Vinland-ed-ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(300,300)}只要心懷堅強確切的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.26,0:23:18.01,Vinland-ed-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(300,300)}時に優しくあればいい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.26,0:23:18.01,Vinland-ed-ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(300,300)}時而保持溫柔之心即可
